{"tid":1376142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推上熱門 請記住 警察調動好撚慢","createTime":"2019-07-28T08:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:00:43.000Z","uid":76975,"like":186,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b1bfb20327c276640e9f88107ab70c0fbe1579cb","tid":1376142,"uid":76975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"利伸 琴日受傷 今日做鍵盤<br />\n<br />\n琴日講完應該一次打兩條線<br />\n邊邊攻到就去邊邊<br />\n今日真係做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住班狗要等上頭order 我地唔洗<br />\n成個過程起碼半個鐘<br />\n見佢地齊裝就退<br />\n退=/=走<br />\n開過第二個戰線等佢地又落gear再上<br />\n無時間食飯<br />\n谷到成身火 無衝突 無得發泄<br />\n我地無手足受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n當然 邊度不設防就玩耐啲<br />\n<br />\n今日 成個港島西 唔好死留一度啦求下你地 ！"},{"pid":"a293fd4fda0c44680bc5d72b75fee87b3ede45b5","tid":1376142,"uid":76975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1dd156c94408d97488abb5a9af61ed5334e054c","tid":1376142,"uid":143382,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n今日冇不反對通知書真係一張好牌要上"},{"pid":"a0c70dbcb064103e08cf310ed2446326a442669a","tid":1376142,"uid":290792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:57:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"876634ede6fd65ce37f44008c558475a9d1f97cc","tid":1376142,"uid":89752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"係一大堆連去邊都唔知的和理非行街之下<br />\n勇武派今日應該可以變隱形戰機"},{"pid":"6bac64c75bd1738d0f3a6a10f3493a40f333a65a","tid":1376142,"uid":288511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n保衛香港游擊戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.